# Evidence Rules

## Submission Requirements
- Link field required on every mission submission.
- For code: Include repo URL, tag or commit, and run steps in README.
- For on-chain work: Include explorer links or NERN links.
- For demos: Include short clip or live URL.
- Proof text limit: 500 characters maximum.
- Screenshots: Up to 5 files, 1 MB each.

## Code Evidence
- Repository must be public or accessible to reviewers.
- Include README with one-command build and run steps.
- Tag or commit hash required for version tracking.
- Tests or CI must pass.

## On-Chain Evidence
- Explorer links must be valid and resolve.
- Transaction hashes must match the claimed action.
- NERN proposal or milestone links must show correct status.

## Demo Evidence
- Live URL must be accessible.
- Video clips should be under 5 minutes.
- Screenshots must show key functionality.